  "detailed_description": "<h1>Siam Twinstick is getting free to play!</h1><p>Soon you can play Siam Twinstick completely for free. So stay tuned!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Pilots, wake up!\r\n\r\nYou are awakened by a strange, godlike creature and your mission is to save the world from evil...\r\n\r\nDo you have the skills to master a badass, adrenaline pumping twinstick-shooter?\r\n\r\n- 22 levels\r\n- 6 boss-fights\r\n- 4 weapons\r\n- Many different enemys\r\n- Highscore system\r\n- Singleplayer or  2 player coop\r\n- 4 difficulty settings (beginner, advanced, expert, insane)\r\n- Full gamepad support\r\n- Mouse/keyboard controlls\r\n- 1080p Resolution\r\n- Many different music tracks",
